  "text": "The main complex event patterns in our work include ALL, ANY, COUNT, and SEQ. In this paper, the COUNT pattern can be used to count the number of vehicles in a specified area during specified time span. The SEQ pattern can be used to represent the moving path of a vehicle. The detailed meaning of the patterns can be found in [CITATION_1] . Those patterns can be composed to create hierarchical complex patterns.",
